Tips

- Use a bold heading to make your project title stand out.
- Provide a brief description of the project and its features.
- Clearly outline the installation and usage steps.
- Mention any requirements and the type of license for your project.

Including this information in your `README.md` file will help users easily understand your project and how to use it.